`x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`DateModified`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`UrlToBrand`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`UserFK`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`KeyId`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`AdvertisePrice`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`DateCreated`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`DateModified`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Height`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`IdOfPosition`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Img`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`PageUrl`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Title`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Width`
FROM `AdvertisementContents` AS `x`
LEFT JOIN `WebMasters` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation` ON `x`.`CensorFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`KeyId`

ORDER BY `x`.`KeyId`

`x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`KeyId`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`AdvertisePrice`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`DateCreated`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`DateModified`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Height`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`IdOfPosition`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Img`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`PageUrl`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Title`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Width`
FROM `AdvertisementContents` AS `x`
LEFT JOIN `WebMasters` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation` ON `x`.`CensorFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`KeyId`
LEFT JOIN `User` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation.UserBy` ON `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`UserFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation.UserBy`.`Id`

INNER JOIN `AdvertisementPositions` AS `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation` ON `x`.`AdvertisementPositionFK` = `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`KeyId`
WHERE `x`.`AdvertiserFK` = @__advertiserId_0
ORDER BY `x`.`KeyId`
LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1" (0723d8ff)

`x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`DateModified`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`UrlToBrand`, `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`UserFK`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`KeyId`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`AdvertisePrice`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`DateCreated`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`PageUrl`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Title`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Width`
FROM `AdvertisementContents` AS `x`
LEFT JOIN `WebMasters` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation` ON `x`.`CensorFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`KeyId`

ORDER BY `x`.`KeyId`
